Plot CO2 Data
=============
[CO2 data](ftp://aftp.cmdl.noaa.gov/products/trends/co2/co2_annmean_mlo.txt)

```{r fig.align='center', out.width=700, out.height=550}
con = 'http://myweb.fsu.edu/jelsner/CO2.txt'
df = read.table(con, header = TRUE)
ggplot(df, aes(x = Year, y = CO2)) +
  geom_line() +
  ylab("Annual CO2 (ppm)") +
  theme_bw()
df2 = data.frame(Year = df$Year[-1], GrowthRate = diff(df$CO2))
ggplot(df2, aes(x = Year, y = GrowthRate)) +
  geom_line() +
  ylab("Annual CO2 Growth Rate (ppm/yr)") +
  theme_bw()
```

